: 1629705709, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2339875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": 2339862, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 本来就是啊", "timestamp": 1629705813, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2339891, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": 2339875, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 没有所谓的本来就是 每个院系都有自己的评定标准 有时间怼我不如怼学校让学校出个解释压死院系", "timestamp": 1629705946, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340042, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "楼上两个别争了。。。我是2018年转系的（六字班大二时降转到七字班），我刚转系的时候奖学金是在转出院系评定的（也就是2018-2019学年秋季学期评定2017-2018学年的奖学金的时候），但从我转系的下一年（2019年）开始就改掉了，之后全部是统一在转入院系评定", "timestamp": 1629707473, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340051, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Eve和Bob各对一半吧。不过我挺好奇Bob如果真的是thuloveu，居然不知道2018年及以前的转系生转出后第一年是在转出院系评奖学金...", "timestamp": 1629707553, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340056, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我一直以为thuloveu是一个年级很高的学长...", "timestamp": 1629707582, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz是零字班的话，辅导员是六字班，估计辅导员是根据他们那时候的经验来判断的。他们那时候确实是跟着原院系一起评🤦🏻‍♀️", "timestamp": 1629708530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢各位道友\n零子班小生 这厢有礼了", "timestamp": 1629708918, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340174, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": 2340128, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 有道理", "timestamp": 1629708929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340349, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": 2340051, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 以前无心学生事务🤭", "timestamp": 1629710957, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340407, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "thuloveu是什么w", "timestamp": 1629711426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2343124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你好，我是电子系奖助辅导员zyd，学生处统一规定，转系学生在转入院系评定奖学金，行政院系与教学院系不一致的，在行政院系评。", "timestamp": 1629735675, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2343134, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 447825, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "原来一直在原院系评，但是很多院系对转出去的学生不友好，所以后来改成转入院系评了。", "timestamp": 1629735758, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 447825, "reply": 29, "tag": null, "text": "求问洞友\n转系之后的奖学金是跟着新院系一起评吗", "timestamp": 1629703105, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629735756, "url": "", "vote": {}}}